Between 20:00 and 02:00 on weekdays, the Grand
Mission's battle points will increase.

Between 02:00 and 11:00 on weekdays, the gold
obtained when defeating enemies will increase.

Between 11:00 and 20:00 on weekdays, the area
points obtained for World/Board Quest completions
will increase.

Between 20:00 and 02:00 on holidays, the Rift
Crystals obtained from Grand Missions will
increase.

Between 02:00 and 11:00 on holidays, the
experience points obtained when defeating enemies
will increase.

Between 11:00 and 20:00 on holidays, the clan
points obtained from clan missions will increase.
